    <h1>Challenge 3:</h1>
    <h2>FizzBuzz</h2>
    <p>
      Write a program that prints the numbers from 1 to 100. For multiples of
      three, print "Fizz" instead of the number, and for multiples of five,
      print "Buzz". For numbers which are multiples of both three and five,
      print "FizzBuzz".
    </p>
    <button id="reveal-button-3">Reveal</button>
    <div class="code-box" id="code-box-3" style="display: none">
      <pre><code>
for i in range(1, 101):
    if i % 3 == 0 and i % 5 == 0:
        print("FizzBuzz")
    elif i % 3 == 0:
        print("Fizz")
    elif i % 5 == 0:
        print("Buzz")
    else:
        print(i)
  </code></pre>
    </div>
